          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " at its production facility and at showrooms around the globe cut into sales, once everything was opened up again business was absolutely booming last year. In fact, Bentley says it recorded the biggest sales numbers in 101 years of the brand’s existence.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
